---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Docs" description="Install, run, and troubleshoot the BridgeAIChat beta.">
  <section class="surface">
    <div class="eyebrow">Documentation</div>
    <h1>From first install to a working multi-device beta setup.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Start with the quickstart for the shortest path. Use the install and tooling guides when you want a cleaner
      control-host setup or a better-tuned remote device.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap grid two">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Start Here</div>
      <h2>Core setup path</h2>
      <div class="doc-links">
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/quickstart">
          <strong>Quickstart</strong>
          Fastest path from fresh install to first reply.
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/install/control-host">
          <strong>Install the control host</strong>
          Run the gateway, set Tailscale API credentials, and open the UI.
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/install/agent">
          <strong>Install an agent device</strong>
          Configure tmux, gateway connectivity, and your local AI CLI.
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Guides</div>
      <h2>Environment-specific help</h2>
      <div class="doc-links">
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/tools/codex">
          <strong>Codex guide</strong>
          Recommended beta path and working assumptions.
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/tools/claude">
          <strong>Claude guide</strong>
          Login, quota, and local-device caveats.
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/networking/tailscale">
          <strong>Tailscale guide</strong>
          Tailnet input, API credentials, and private agent routing.
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/troubleshooting">
          <strong>Troubleshooting</strong>
          Fix the most common setup and runtime failures.
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
